text.tspan: • As label for class c arrives, learn one-vs-all modulations
on top of frozen feedforward weights.
• The orthogonal projection loss collapses samples of class c,
and orthogonalizes these samples from other samples.
• Use contrastive learning with different positives
to achieve different invariances (e.g. Barlow Twins):
